You may only upgrade from 1.5.3b.  

Execute upgrade.sql as the root user:

mysql -uroot < upgrade.sql

You should see the following:
======== [cut] =========

Adding new aggregate function types to the flexviews metadata

Update any STDDEV expressions to be STDDEV_POP expression (same result, different name)

Removing ability to add new STDDEV expressions (use STDDEV_POP)

Installing stored procedures
message
If you see no errors, then installation was successful.

upgrade done.

======= [/cut] =========

Report any problems to the bug tracker.
